        Airbnb and Short-Stay Rentals in Brisbane Body Corporate Buildings: What Unit Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Whether your building permits short-term letting is determined by the body corporate's by-laws and it directly shapes who will buy your unit and for how much.
      </p>
